    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/98e98a90781cec2f20092f42acb40bca847eff6f0790262dcd95918fa03f7795.jpg",
        "image_caption": [
            "Output Image "
        ],
        "image_footnote": [],
        "bbox": [
            598,
            782,
            873,
            883
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "八、 Image Alignment（图像队列）",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            144,
            101,
            505,
            122
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "默认情况下，复制区域工具将输入图像的输入区域复制到目标图像的左上角，如下图所",
        "bbox": [
            144,
            130,
            847,
            165
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "示: ",
        "bbox": [
            181,
            168,
            208,
            181
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/6b1dfa2a7a14f9443e9f5581ee0e69db2ef4db7607926d032f5a3d7c21fcaac1.jpg",
        "image_caption": [
            "Input Image with Input Region "
        ],
        "image_footnote": [],
        "bbox": [
            196,
            218,
            453,
            355
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/f1e72fcf9d4d9d9c315cfc95364cc97bc4cf74e9e12055071932a1cf697af112.jpg",
        "image_caption": [
            "Output Image "
        ],
        "image_footnote": [],
        "bbox": [
            480,
            218,
            751,
            362
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "将输入区域的内容复制到目标图像的大多数应用程序都需要为复制操作定义对齐方式。",
        "bbox": [
            181,
            388,
            847,
            406
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "通过启用对齐，您可以精确地控制工具在目标图像中复制输入区域的位置，因为该工",
        "bbox": [
            181,
            407,
            847,
            424
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "具",
        "bbox": [
            146,
            426,
            169,
            442
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "允许您定义图像坐标，该工具将使用该坐标在复制操作之前对齐输入图像和目标图像。",
        "bbox": [
            181,
            445,
